Sources/LiteRTLM/
    The thin Swift wrapper around the LiteRT-LM C API. Vendored verbatim from
    google-ai-edge/litert-lm, release v0.13.1, licensed under the Apache
    License, Version 2.0. Original copyright Google LLC. See each file's header
    and the LICENSE file at the repository root.

    We vendor these files (rather than depending on the upstream SwiftPM
    package) so the package resolves without git-lfs: the upstream repository
    LFS-tracks Android/Linux/Windows prebuilt libraries that are irrelevant to
    Apple platforms but make `swift package resolve` fragile.

CLiteRTLM.xcframework / CLiteRTLM_mac.xcframework
    Prebuilt native runtime binaries downloaded at build time from the official
    LiteRT-LM GitHub releases (v0.13.1). Copyright Google LLC, Apache-2.0.
    Not redistributed in this repository.

